text.tspan: Need motivated trumpet and trombone for brass band (Flagstaff)
We are a local brass band, since 2021, mostly playing American pop covers (The Killers, Lady Gaga, etc).
Instrumentation last year was drums, saxes, trumpets, trombones, sousaphone.
Some trumpets/trombones have recently quit the band, so I'm looking for replacements.
Do you know any trumpet/trombone players in town who may like to play in a brass band,
can memorize melody lines of easy pop songs, and don't have too many other committments?
(seems like the former trumpet players are all playing with a bunch of other bands
so they don't have time for the brass band project --
would be nice to recruit somebody who is not playing with a ton of other bands currently)
Goal is to get together and play about once per week, either
2. practicing Sunday evenings at NAU, or
3. playing gigs at various places nearby (Orpheum, bars, etc)
